The '''Religious Research Association''' is a scholarly association of researchers and religious professionals.<ref name="rra">[http://rra.hartsem.edu/abouttheRRA.htm Official website]</ref><ref name="encyclopedia">[http://hirr.hartsem.edu/ency/RRA.htm Encyclopedia of Religion and Society]</ref>
